#=====================================#
#          Server config              #
#=====================================#

Backup for configurations and lists of packages required.

Installs & configures:
- Web server (Nginx, PHP5, memcached, MySQL)
- Shorewall firewall & DHCP
- Transmission
- ProFTPd
- PECL & PEAR packages
- Samba

Requirements:
- Ubuntu server (might still work on Debian)
- Dual network interfaces
- Git
